00:10:18,290 --> 00:10:21,680
and I think the formal English translation
was like a sense of doom,

199
00:10:21,680 --> 00:10:24,430
of impending doom about the country.

200
00:10:24,430 --> 00:10:25,880
But that's kind of how a lot of young people

201
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:28,290
have felt about this upcoming election,

202
00:10:28,290 --> 00:10:31,710
because of the KMT's kind of a return to popularity.

203
00:10:31,710 --> 00:10:35,970
Well, so what's making people go back to the
KMT?

