00:11:21,350 --> 00:11:24,890
or they voted for the DPP instead.

221
00:11:24,890 --> 00:11:28,580
And a lot of that kind of common sentiment
just isn't around anymore.

222
00:11:28,580 --> 00:11:32,690
Meanwhile, a lot of KMT voters have really
mobilized

